---
// 競合差別化マトリクスセクション
---

<section class="py-16 bg-gray-50">
  <div class="max-w-7xl mx-auto px-4 sm:px-6 lg:px-8">
    <div class="text-center mb-12">
      <h2 class="text-4xl font-bold text-gray-900 mb-4">
        業界唯一の成果保証モデル
      </h2>
      <p class="text-xl text-gray-600 max-w-3xl mx-auto">
        他社との違いを明確に比較。リスクなしで確実な成果を提供する唯一のサービス
      </p>
    </div>

    <!-- 比較表 -->
    <div class="bg-white rounded-xl shadow-lg overflow-hidden">
      <div class="overflow-x-auto">
        <table class="w-full">
          <thead class="bg-gradient-to-r from-blue-600 to-green-600 text-white">
            <tr>
              <th class="px-6 py-4 text-left font-semibold">比較項目</th>
              <th class="px-6 py-4 text-center font-semibold">
                <div class="flex flex-col items-center">
                  <span class="text-lg font-bold">BoltSite</span>
                  <span class="text-sm opacity-90">(Cor.inc)</span>
                </div>
              </th>
              <th class="px-6 py-4 text-center font-semibold">WordPress制作</th>
              <th class="px-6 py-4 text-center font-semibold">大手制作会社</th>
              <th class="px-6 py-4 text-center font-semibold">フリーランス</th>
            </tr>
          </thead>
          <tbody class="divide-y divide-gray-200">
            <!-- 初期費用 -->
            <tr class="hover:bg-gray-50">
              <td class="px-6 py-4 font-semibold text-gray-900">初期費用</td>
              <td class="px-6 py-4 text-center">
                <span class="bg-green-100 text-green-800 px-3 py-1 rounded-full text-sm font-semibold">0円</span>
              </td>
              <td class="px-6 py-4 text-center text-gray-600">30万円〜</td>
              <td class="px-6 py-4 text-center text-gray-600">100万円〜</td>
              <td class="px-6 py-4 text-center text-gray-600">20万円〜</td>
            </tr>

            <!-- 成果保証 -->
            <tr class="hover:bg-gray-50 bg-blue-50">
              <td class="px-6 py-4 font-semibold text-gray-900">成果保証</td>
              <td class="px-6 py-4 text-center">
                <span class="bg-blue-100 text-blue-800 px-3 py-1 rounded-full text-sm font-semibold">あり（返金付き）</span>
              </td>
              <td class="px-6 py-4 text-center text-red-600">なし</td>
              <td class="px-6 py-4 text-center text-red-600">なし</td>
              <td class="px-6 py-4 text-center text-red-600">なし</td>
            </tr>

            <!-- 契約縛り -->
            <tr class="hover:bg-gray-50">
              <td class="px-6 py-4 font-semibold text-gray-900">契約縛り</td>
              <td class="px-6 py-4 text-center">
                <span class="bg-green-100 text-green-800 px-3 py-1 rounded-full text-sm font-semibold">6ヶ月</span>
              </td>
              <td class="px-6 py-4 text-center text-gray-600">なし〜1年</td>
              <td class="px-6 py-4 text-center text-gray-600">1年〜</td>
              <td class="px-6 py-4 text-center text-gray-600">なし〜6ヶ月</td>
            </tr>

            <!-- 表示速度 -->
            <tr class="hover:bg-gray-50">
              <td class="px-6 py-4 font-semibold text-gray-900">表示速度</td>
              <td class="px-6 py-4 text-center">
                <span class="bg-green-100 text-green-800 px-3 py-1 rounded-full text-sm font-semibold">0.3秒</span>
              </td>
              <td class="px-6 py-4 text-center text-red-600">3-10秒</td>
              <td class="px-6 py-4 text-center text-yellow-600">1-3秒</td>
              <td class="px-6 py-4 text-center text-yellow-600">1-5秒</td>
            </tr>

            <!-- 保証内容 -->
            <tr class="hover:bg-gray-50 bg-blue-50">
              <td class="px-6 py-4 font-semibold text-gray-900">保証内容</td>
              <td class="px-6 py-4 text-center">
                <span class="bg-blue-100 text-blue-800 px-3 py-1 rounded-full text-sm font-semibold">数値目標明確</span>
              </td>
              <td class="px-6 py-4 text-center text-red-600">なし</td>
              <td class="px-6 py-4 text-center text-gray-600">SLAのみ</td>
              <td class="px-6 py-4 text-center text-red-600">なし</td>
            </tr>

            <!-- 技術サポート -->
            <tr class="hover:bg-gray-50">
              <td class="px-6 py-4 font-semibold text-gray-900">技術サポート</td>
              <td class="px-6 py-4 text-center">
                <span class="bg-green-100 text-green-800 px-3 py-1 rounded-full text-sm font-semibold">専任チーム</span>
              </td>
              <td class="px-6 py-4 text-center text-gray-600">限定的</td>
              <td class="px-6 py-4 text-center text-gray-600">担当者制</td>
              <td class="px-6 py-4 text-center text-yellow-600">個人対応</td>
            </tr>

            <!-- スケーラビリティ -->
            <tr class="hover:bg-gray-50">
              <td class="px-6 py-4 font-semibold text-gray-900">スケーラビリティ</td>
              <td class="px-6 py-4 text-center">
                <span class="bg-green-100 text-green-800 px-3 py-1 rounded-full text-sm font-semibold">無制限</span>
              </td>
              <td class="px-6 py-4 text-center text-yellow-600">サーバー依存</td>
              <td class="px-6 py-4 text-center text-gray-600">高コスト</td>
              <td class="px-6 py-4 text-center text-yellow-600">技術依存</td>
            </tr>

            <!-- セキュリティ -->
            <tr class="hover:bg-gray-50">
              <td class="px-6 py-4 font-semibold text-gray-900">セキュリティ</td>
              <td class="px-6 py-4 text-center">
                <span class="bg-green-100 text-green-800 px-3 py-1 rounded-full text-sm font-semibold">企業レベル</span>
              </td>
              <td class="px-6 py-4 text-center text-red-600">脆弱性リスク</td>
              <td class="px-6 py-4 text-center text-gray-600">標準的</td>
              <td class="px-6 py-4 text-center text-yellow-600">技術依存</td>
            </tr>

            <!-- 月額コスト -->
            <tr class="hover:bg-gray-50 bg-green-50">
              <td class="px-6 py-4 font-semibold text-gray-900">月額コスト</td>
              <td class="px-6 py-4 text-center">
                <span class="bg-green-100 text-green-800 px-3 py-1 rounded-full text-sm font-semibold">15,000円〜</span>
              </td>
              <td class="px-6 py-4 text-center text-gray-600">5,000円〜</td>
              <td class="px-6 py-4 text-center text-red-600">50,000円〜</td>
              <td class="px-6 py-4 text-center text-gray-600">10,000円〜</td>
            </tr>
          </tbody>
        </table>
      </div>
    </div>

    <!-- 成果保証の詳細 -->
    <div class="mt-12 grid md:grid-cols-3 gap-8">
      <div class="bg-white rounded-xl shadow-lg p-6 text-center">
        <div class="bg-blue-100 w-16 h-16 rounded-full flex items-center justify-center mx-auto mb-4">
          <svg class="w-8 h-8 text-blue-600" fill="none" stroke="currentColor" viewBox="0 0 24 24">
            <path stroke-linecap="round" stroke-linejoin="round" stroke-width="2" d="M9 12l2 2 4-4m6 2a9 9 0 11-18 0 9 9 0 0118 0z"></path>
          </svg>
        </div>
        <h3 class="text-xl font-bold text-gray-900 mb-2">技術保証</h3>
        <p class="text-gray-600 mb-4">PageSpeed 85点以上を3ヶ月で保証</p>
        <div class="text-sm text-red-600 font-semibold">未達成なら50%返金</div>
      </div>

      <div class="bg-white rounded-xl shadow-lg p-6 text-center">
        <div class="bg-green-100 w-16 h-16 rounded-full flex items-center justify-center mx-auto mb-4">
          <svg class="w-8 h-8 text-green-600" fill="none" stroke="currentColor" viewBox="0 0 24 24">
            <path stroke-linecap="round" stroke-linejoin="round" stroke-width="2" d="M13 10V3L4 14h7v7l9-11h-7z"></path>
          </svg>
        </div>
        <h3 class="text-xl font-bold text-gray-900 mb-2">ビジネス保証</h3>
        <p class="text-gray-600 mb-4">具体的な数値改善を6ヶ月で保証</p>
        <div class="text-sm text-orange-600 font-semibold">未達成なら30%返金</div>
      </div>

      <div class="bg-white rounded-xl shadow-lg p-6 text-center">
        <div class="bg-purple-100 w-16 h-16 rounded-full flex items-center justify-center mx-auto mb-4">
          <svg class="w-8 h-8 text-purple-600" fill="none" stroke="currentColor" viewBox="0 0 24 24">
            <path stroke-linecap="round" stroke-linejoin="round" stroke-width="2" d="M12 8c-1.657 0-3 .895-3 2s1.343 2 3 2 3 .895 3 2-1.343 2-3 2m0-8c1.11 0 2.08.402 2.599 1M12 8V7m0 1v8m0 0v1m0-1c-1.11 0-2.08-.402-2.599-1"></path>
          </svg>
        </div>
        <h3 class="text-xl font-bold text-gray-900 mb-2">柔軟な契約</h3>
        <p class="text-gray-600 mb-4">6ヶ月後は3つの選択肢から自由選択</p>
        <div class="text-sm text-blue-600 font-semibold">1年縛りなし</div>
      </div>
    </div>

    <!-- 顧客メリットの比較 -->
    <div class="mt-12 bg-gradient-to-r from-blue-50 to-green-50 rounded-xl p-8">
      <h3 class="text-2xl font-bold text-center text-gray-900 mb-8">顧客メリットの比較</h3>
      <div class="grid md:grid-cols-2 gap-8">
        <div>
          <h4 class="text-lg font-semibold text-gray-900 mb-4">従来のリスク</h4>
          <ul class="space-y-2 text-gray-600">
            <li class="flex items-center">
              <svg class="w-5 h-5 text-red-500 mr-3" fill="currentColor" viewBox="0 0 20 20">
                <path fill-rule="evenodd" d="M8.257 3.099c.765-1.36 2.722-1.36 3.486 0l5.58 9.92c.75 1.334-.213 2.98-1.742 2.98H4.42c-1.53 0-2.493-1.646-1.743-2.98l5.58-9.92zM11 13a1 1 0 11-2 0 1 1 0 012 0zm-1-8a1 1 0 00-1 1v3a1 1 0 002 0V6a1 1 0 00-1-1z" clip-rule="evenodd"></path>
              </svg>
              最大リスク：18万円〜（1年分）
            </li>
            <li class="flex items-center">
              <svg class="w-5 h-5 text-red-500 mr-3" fill="currentColor" viewBox="0 0 20 20">
                <path fill-rule="evenodd" d="M8.257 3.099c.765-1.36 2.722-1.36 3.486 0l5.58 9.92c.75 1.334-.213 2.98-1.742 2.98H4.42c-1.53 0-2.493-1.646-1.743-2.98l5.58-9.92zM11 13a1 1 0 11-2 0 1 1 0 012 0zm-1-8a1 1 0 00-1 1v3a1 1 0 002 0V6a1 1 0 00-1-1z" clip-rule="evenodd"></path>
              </svg>
              解約可能時期：1年後
            </li>
            <li class="flex items-center">
              <svg class="w-5 h-5 text-red-500 mr-3" fill="currentColor" viewBox="0 0 20 20">
                <path fill-rule="evenodd" d="M8.257 3.099c.765-1.36 2.722-1.36 3.486 0l5.58 9.92c.75 1.334-.213 2.98-1.742 2.98H4.42c-1.53 0-2.493-1.646-1.743-2.98l5.58-9.92zM11 13a1 1 0 11-2 0 1 1 0 012 0zm-1-8a1 1 0 00-1 1v3a1 1 0 002 0V6a1 1 0 00-1-1z" clip-rule="evenodd"></path>
              </svg>
              失敗時の保証：なし
            </li>
          </ul>
        </div>
        <div>
          <h4 class="text-lg font-semibold text-gray-900 mb-4">BoltSiteの改善</h4>
          <ul class="space-y-2 text-gray-600">
            <li class="flex items-center">
              <svg class="w-5 h-5 text-green-500 mr-3" fill="currentColor" viewBox="0 0 20 20">
                <path fill-rule="evenodd" d="M16.707 5.293a1 1 0 010 1.414l-8 8a1 1 0 01-1.414 0l-4-4a1 1 0 011.414-1.414L8 12.586l7.293-7.293a1 1 0 011.414 0z" clip-rule="evenodd"></path>
              </svg>
              最大リスク：9万円〜（6ヶ月分）<span class="text-green-600 font-semibold ml-2">50%削減</span>
            </li>
            <li class="flex items-center">
              <svg class="w-5 h-5 text-green-500 mr-3" fill="currentColor" viewBox="0 0 20 20">
                <path fill-rule="evenodd" d="M16.707 5.293a1 1 0 010 1.414l-8 8a1 1 0 01-1.414 0l-4-4a1 1 0 011.414-1.414L8 12.586l7.293-7.293a1 1 0 011.414 0z" clip-rule="evenodd"></path>
              </svg>
              解約可能時期：6ヶ月後<span class="text-green-600 font-semibold ml-2">6ヶ月短縮</span>
            </li>
            <li class="flex items-center">
              <svg class="w-5 h-5 text-green-500 mr-3" fill="currentColor" viewBox="0 0 20 20">
                <path fill-rule="evenodd" d="M16.707 5.293a1 1 0 010 1.414l-8 8a1 1 0 01-1.414 0l-4-4a1 1 0 011.414-1.414L8 12.586l7.293-7.293a1 1 0 011.414 0z" clip-rule="evenodd"></path>
              </svg>
              失敗時の保証：最大50%返金<span class="text-green-600 font-semibold ml-2">実質リスク45,000円〜</span>
            </li>
          </ul>
        </div>
      </div>
    </div>
  </div>
</section>
